.SH NAME
messages - quick count of messages in mailbox or folder
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B messages
.br
.B messages
folder-name
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Messages
counts the occurances of "^From\ " in either the current incoming
mailbox or the specified folder.
.P
This is, in fact, a simple little shell script!!
